original_title: All About Eve - Live in Bonn 1991
overview: Live in Bonn 1991 is a concert DVD from the British alternative rock band All About Eve. The DVD comprises the full September 5 live concert at the Biskuithalle in Bonne, Germany, part of the band's 1991 European tour promoting their recently-released album, Touched by Jesus. The footage was originally recorded for the German music television programme Rockpalast.
title: All About Eve Live in Bonn 1991
